### 4. 动画资源

**Sprite 模式**（默认）

- 资源：`src/spritesheet.webp`
- 帧映射：`src/validation.json`
- 涵盖状态：`idle` / `running-right` / `running-left` / `waving` / `jumping` / `failed` / `waiting` / `running` / `review` / `chatting` / `fetching` / `searching` / `analyzing` / `building` / `celebrating` / `sleeping`
- 控制器：[`src/sprite-animator.js`](file:///d:/project file/Desktop_Pet/src/sprite-animator.js)

**GIF 模式**（备用，按 `Ctrl+G` 切换）

- 控制器：[`src/gif-animator.js`](file:///d:/project file/Desktop_Pet/src/gif-animator.js)
- `stateMap` 映射：
  ```js
  'idle'      → idle1.gif
  'waving'    → idle1.gif
  'jumping'   → idle1.gif
  'running'   → move.gif
  'drag'      → drag.gif
  'screen1'   ~ 'screen7' → screenN.gif
  ```

